-Hey.

225
00:23:22,861 --> 00:23:24,363
Quiet.

226
00:23:26,698 --> 00:23:28,367
Stand by.

227
00:23:44,883 --> 00:23:46,260
Let's go.

228
00:24:39,271 --> 00:24:42,983
<i>The most inquisitive creature
in Africa is the baboon.</i>

229
00:25:02,794 --> 00:25:05,589
<i>Xi said,
"That is a very evil thing you've got.</i>

230
00:25:06,173 --> 00:25:09,885
<i>You better give it back so I can
take it and throw it off the earth.</i>

231
00:25:10,093 --> 00:25:13,597
<i>It brought unhappiness to my family.
