00:51:10,863 --> 00:51:13,198
Stop! Stop, stop, stop! Stop!

422
00:51:16,368 --> 00:51:18,078
<i>Frank?</i>

423
00:51:18,287 --> 00:51:21,164
<i>Frank? Frank, what was that noise?</i>

424
00:51:21,874 --> 00:51:24,168
